  <text name="introHelp" >
    <page>
      <p>[UFO Attack]</p>
      <p>
        Test / BETA. I hope you enjoy it, and feedback and info at http://code.google.com/p/unflobtactical/.
      </p>
      <p> The buttons on the lower right navigate help, the lower left exits help.</p>
      <p>'New' starts a new game. The game auto-saves at exit and you can resume your current game with 'Continue'.</p>
    </page>
    <page>
      <p>[Status]</p>
      <p>The tactical game is fully playable. Feedback on gameplay, pacing, difficulty, and bugs is especially valuable. 
      </p>
      <p>UI is near-final.</p>
      <p>Model, texture, and map art is placeholder.</p>
      <p>The geoscape (strategic) game is completely missing.</p>
    </page>
  </text>


